    • getDetailedCompatibility

      public java.lang.String getDetailedCompatibility()
      Get the summary of detailed compatibility

      The detailed algorithm is composed of two parts - numerology and astrology. If horoscope of the person to be matched is not sure, the score will be calculated purely by life path number compatibility. Otherwise, the score will be calculated by 60% of horoscope compatibility and 40% of life path number compatibility.

      Returns:
      Summary of detailed compatibility

    • getHoroscopeExplanation

      public java.lang.String getHoroscopeExplanation()
      Get the summary of horoscope explanation

      If horoscope of the person to be matched is not sure, the returned summary will only include the meaning of the user's horoscope element. Otherwise, the returned summary will include the meaning of both the user and the partner's horoscope element, and some advice for their relationship.

      Zodiac Compatibility and zodiac sign meaning is referenced from
      https://www.elitedaily.com/life/zodiac-signs-element-can-actually-reveal-compatibility/2064007
      https://www.thecut.com/article/how-to-understand-every-zodiac-sign-by-element.html

      Returns:
      Summary of horoscope explanation

    • getChineseZodiacRecommendation

      public java.lang.String getChineseZodiacRecommendation()
      Get the summary of Chinese zodiac recommendation

      User's Chinese zodiac sign is generated based on the provided birth year. The returned summary shows what Chinese zodiac sign will be most compatible to the user. Based on the age preference selected by user, the summary will suggest 2-4 birth years that will be compatible to the user.

      Chinese Zodiac Compatibility is referenced from
      https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chinese_zodiac
      https://www.travelchinaguide.com/intro/social_customs/zodiac/compatibility.htm

      Returns:
      Summary of Chinese zodiac recommendation

    • getDetailedReport

      public void getDetailedReport()
      Generate a full report showing the detailed compatibility. A dialog will pop up.
